<div class="askContLeft w715">
        <div class="answerLeft">
          <p class="til fz24" id="title">我们应该怎么样去做期货？</p>
          <p class="time"><em><i>2018-01-29 20:57:42&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阅读333人</i></em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;作者：信鑫资讯 </p>
          <div class="answerText">
            <div class="answerTextCont break">
              
            <p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;text-indent:28px;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">在期货交易过程中，很多情形下，都需要休息和调整：</span></strong>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">1、当趋势不明，价格无序波动时，只能耐心等待价格的突破和趋势的明朗；</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">2、当自己看不明白，对行情的演变心中无底时，最好不要轻易介入。行情经常有，如果没有弄明白就一头扎进去，很可能就站错了队，搞错了方向，所以必须只做自己感觉有把握的行情；</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">3、当做反方向时，很多投资者习惯于立即反手。如果价格稍微反向修正，他可能被迫止损。因为思维的惯性作用，他对调转方向心中本来就没底。其实，在这样的情况下，应该先停下来，将做错方向的仓位及时退出，给自己留出一段时间调整思维，然后再决定是否反手操作。这和开车调头是一个道理，没有缓冲过程陡然调头，非翻车不可；</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">4、当交易连续亏损，交易节奏紊乱时，及时停下来调整心态，是非常必要的，不然会越来越乱。就像跳交谊舞，一旦舞步踏乱了，总踩舞伴的脚，就只能就地停下来，等踏准舞曲节拍后再和舞伴起跳；</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">5、 当出现大亏后，很多交易者希望赶紧翻本，最后越亏越惨，血本无归。就像输急了眼的赌徒一样，将最后所有的筹码都押上。其实这时候最需要的是离开市场，有一个疗伤过程，并总结造成亏损的原因，等休养生息恢复自信后，再返回市场也不迟。</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">6、当交易状态异常时，及时罢手修整。相信每个人都有自己的"运气週期"，当某一段时间诸事不顺，感觉不好，伸手就被咬时，表明自己处于"揹运"期，如果勉强做单交易，很可能接连失利。当一连作单都不顺时，请适时休息一下，先离场，让自己先放松。</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;"><br />
</span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;"><img src="/upload/Image/20180129/20180129205938_47705.jpg" alt="" /></span>
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;"></span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;text-indent:27px;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">做金融，就要像一个狙击手一样</span></strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">：</span></strong>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">第一、目标明确，目标不明确绝不出手。</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">第二</span>,</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">确定好目标，就要制定好详细的切实可行的行动计划。</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">第三，</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">要把自己隐藏好，绝不能外漏，否则等于自杀。</span>
</p>
<p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:#3E3E3E;font-family:&quot;font-size:16px;line-height:25.6px;white-space:normal;widows:1;background-color:#FFFFFF;box-sizing:border-box !important;">
	<span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">第四，</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;">行动时，必须要稳、准、狠。第四、要保证能全身而退。做金融和狙击一样，金融的操作同样要明确的行情判断、做单计划、同样对待大行情要稳、准、狠，抓住机会就大赚一票。判断失误就要止损，保证全身而退。轻易不出手</span>,一出手就中</span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box !important;word-wrap:break-word !important;font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0px;font-size:13px;">。</span>
</p> 
			  
